⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Beck
node TRN · TRN · ⟦Beck:TRN:85e7bc⟧

WHO   — Beck — the renegade · the Grid's hope
WHAT  — The hero of TRON: Uprising: an everyprogram who takes up the disc and the mantle to fight for a Grid under tyranny.
WHERE — TRN · TRON  Framework inputs: TRON (Disney, 1982–2025)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the occupation between the films needed a face — a made thing choosing rebellion and the Users' creed.
HOW   — By a mechanic's skill, TRON's training, and the borrowed identity of the Renegade to give the Grid hope.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  TRON trained me to be the Renegade — one program standing for all of them, so the Grid would remember it could resist.

